Total mortality z

z-methods.Rd

Returns the calculation of total mortality, z, usually as the sum of fishing mortality, f, and natural mortality, m.

z(object, ...)

# S4 method for FLS
z(object, ...)

Arguments

object

Object to calculate on.

Value

An object of the corresponding class, usually FLQuant.

See also

FLQuant

Examples

data(ple4)
